===Symbol===
'''≡'''
#{{mathematics}} is [[equivalent]] to
#{{mathematics}} is [[identically]] [[equal]] to
#:''The [[function]]s f and g satisfies f≡g [[iff]] their respective [[domain of definition]] coincide, and if f(x)=g(x) for all x in this domain''
# (''number theory'') is [[congruent]] to; used in calculations of [[modulo]].
#:''15≡3 mod 4, since both 15 and 3 gives a remainder of 3 when divided by 4.''
#{{chemistry}} A [[triple bond]].

